FengYi2009 is an open source project which intends to implement a real-time communication software
for generic purpose. It should be portable between LINUX and Windows OS.

Feng: a kind of tower, the ancient Chinese military force used it to communicate by smoking on top of it
Yi  : post-horse, the ancient Chinese used it to deliver mails
 
Author: DreamFreelancer
email : zhangxb66@2008.sina.com
Date  : 2009-4-28

Conventions in this projects:
====prefix====
====surfix==== 
_t: type or class
_tt: type template
_it: interface or abstrast class

====locale====
utf-8 is applied through this project

